{"title_page": "U.S. Route 5 in Massachusetts", "text_new": "{{highway detail hatnote|U.S. Route 5}}\n{{infobox road\n|state=MA\n|type=US\n|route=5\n|map={{maplink|frame=yes|plain=yes|frame-align=center|frame-width=290|frame-height=290|type=line|raw={{Wikipedia:Map data/Wikipedia KML/U.S. Route 5 in Massachusetts}}}}\n|map_custom=yes\n|map_notes=US 5 highlighted in red\n|length_mi=53.46\n|length_ref=<ref name=\"Google Maps US 5 MA\">{{google maps|url=https://maps.google.com/maps?saddr=US-7+N&daddr=US-7+N%2FSimonds+Rd&hl=en&sll=42.724695,-73.201904&sspn=0.068097,0.168743&geocode=FZuZgQIdrSOh-w%3BFdQ7jAIdWtui-w&t=h&mra=ls&z=9|title=U.S. Route 7 in Massachusetts|accessdate=2014-01-22}}</ref>\n|established=\n|direction_a=South\n|direction_b=North\n|terminus_a={{Jct|state=CT|US|5}} in [[Enfield, Connecticut|Enfield, CT]]\n|junction={{plainlist|\n*{{jct|state=MA|I|91}} in [[Springfield, Massachusetts|Springfield]]\n*{{jct|state=MA|MA|57}} in [[Agawam, Massachusetts|Agawam]]\n*{{jct|state=MA|US|20}} in [[West Springfield, Massachusetts|West Springfield]]\n*{{jct|state=MA|I|91|I|90}} in West Springfield\n*{{jct|state=MA|US|202}} in [[Holyoke, Massachusetts|Holyoke]]\n*{{jct|state=MA|MA|9|MA|10}} in [[Northampton, Massachusetts|Northampton]]\n*{{jct|state=MA|MA|2}} in [[Greenfield, Massachusetts|Greenfield]]\n*{{jct|state=MA|MA|10}} in [[Bernardston, Massachusetts|Bernardston]]\n}}\n|terminus_b={{Jct|state=VT|US|5}} in [[Guilford, Vermont|Guilford, VT]]\n|counties=[[Hampden County, Massachusetts|Hampden]], [[Hampshire County, Massachusetts|Hampshire]], [[Franklin County, Massachusetts|Franklin]]\n|previous_type=MA\n|previous_route=4\n|next_type=US\n|next_route=5A\n}}\n\n'''U.S. Route&nbsp;5''' ('''US&nbsp;5''') is a north\u2013south [[U.S. Highway]] extending from southern [[Connecticut]] to the northernmost part of [[Vermont]]. In [[Massachusetts]], the route travels {{convert|53.5|mi}}, paralleling the [[Connecticut River]] and [[Interstate 91 in Massachusetts|Interstate 91]] (I-91) through [[Hampden County, Massachusetts|Hampden]], [[Hampshire County, Massachusetts|Hampshire]], and [[Franklin County, Massachusetts|Franklin]] counties.\n\n==Route description==\nUS&nbsp;5 stays very close to the [[Connecticut River]] and [[Interstate 91]]. It enters the state at the town of [[Longmeadow, Massachusetts|Longmeadow]] on the east bank of the river going up to [[Springfield, Massachusetts|Springfield]]. In Springfield, US&nbsp;5 then overlaps with [[Interstate 91 in Massachusetts|Interstate 91]] (I-91) for about {{convert|0.5|mi|km}}, then separates as its own freeway crossing the Connecticut River on the South End Bridge into [[Agawam, Massachusetts|Agawam]]. The freeway portion travels for about {{convert|3.3|mi|km}} up to [[West Springfield, Massachusetts|West Springfield]]. From the town of [[Northampton, Massachusetts|Northampton]] up to [[Bernardston, Massachusetts|Bernardston]], US&nbsp;5 travels [[Concurrency (road)|concurrent]] with [[Massachusetts Route&nbsp;10]] (Route&nbsp;10 for {{convert|26|mi|km}}. US&nbsp;5 also passes through [[Holyoke, Massachusetts|Holyoke]], [[Hatfield, Massachusetts|Hatfield]], [[Whately, Massachusetts|Whately]], [[Deerfield, Massachusetts|Deerfield]], and [[Greenfield, Massachusetts|Greenfield]]. As in Connecticut, and Vermont US&nbsp;5 has many interchanges with the parallel I-91.\n{{Clear}}\n\n==Major intersections==\n{{mileposts}}\n{{jcttop|state=MA|length_ref=<ref name=\"Google Maps US 5 MA\"/>}}\n{{MAint\n|county=Hampden\n|cspan=15\n|location=Longmeadow\n|lspan=2\n|mile=0.00\n|road={{jct|state=CT|US|5|dir1=south|city1=Enfield|city2=Hartford}}\n|notes=Continuation into [[Connecticut]]}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=1.80\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|192|dir1=south|city1=East Longmeadow|location2=[[Stafford Springs, CT]]}}\n|notes=Northern terminus of Route 192}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Springfield\n|lspan=3\n|mile=3.50\n|type=concur\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=south|location1=[[Hartford, CT]]}}\n|notes=Southern terminus of concurrency with I-91; Exit 1 on I-91}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=3.70\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|83|dir1=south|city1=Forest Park|city2=East Longmeadow}}\n|notes=Northern terminus of Route 83; Exit 2 on I-91}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=3.90\n|type=concur\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=north|city1=Greenfield}}\n|notes=Northern terminus of concurrency with I-91; Exit 3 on I-91}}\n{{jctbridge\n|location_special=[[Connecticut River]]\n|mile=\n|bridge=[[South End Bridge (Massachusetts)|South End Bridge]]}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Agawam\n|mile=4.60\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|57|dir1=west|city1=Agawam|city2=Southwick}}\n|notes=Rotary interchange; Eastern terminus of Route&nbsp;57}}\n{{MAint\n|location=West Springfield\n|lspan=4\n|mile=5.80\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|147|dir1=west|city1=West Springfield|city2=Agawam}}\n|notes=Rotary interchange; Eastern terminus of Route&nbsp;147, to [[Memorial Bridge (Massachusetts)|Memorial Bridge]]}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=7.00\n|road={{jct|state=MA|US|20|city1=Westfield|city2=Springfield}}\n|notes=Rotary interchange}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=9.30\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|I|391|to2=yes|city1=Holyoke}}\n|notes=Exit 10 on I-91 (formerly exit 13)}}\n{{MAint\n|type=toll\n|mile=10.80\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|I|90|city1=Holyoke|location2=[[Springfield, Massachusetts|Springfield]]|city3=Boston|location4=[[Albany, New York|Albany, NY]]}}\n|notes=Exit 45 on I-90 (formerly exit 4); Exit 11 on I-91 (formerly exit 14)}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Holyoke\n|lspan=4\n|mile=13.80\n|road={{jct|state=MA|US|202|I|91|to2=yes|city1=Westfield|city2=Southwick|city3=South Hadley}}\n|notes=}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=14.60\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|141|dir1=east|city1=Holyoke Center|city2=Chicopee Falls}}\n|notes=One-way eastbound}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=14.80\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|141|dir1=west|city1=Easthampton|I|91|to2=yes}}\n|notes=One-way westbound}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=15.00\n|road={{jct|state=MA|US|202|to1=yes|city1=South Hadley Falls|city2=Athol}}\n|notes=Via Lincoln Street}}\n{{MAint\n|county=Hampshire\n|cspan=5\n|location=Northampton\n|lspan=4\n|mile=21.90\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|city1=Greenfield|city3=Springfield}}\n|notes=Exit 23 on I-91 (formerly exit 18)}}\n{{MAint\n|type=concur\n|mile=22.90\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|9|MA|10|dir2=south|city1=Easthampton|city2=Pittsfield|city3=Amherst|city4=Worcester}}\n|notes=Southern terminus of concurrency with Route 10}}\n{{MAint\n|type=incomplete\n|mile=24.30\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=north|city1=Greenfield}}\n|notes=Northbound exit and southbound entrance; Exit 26 on I-91 (formerly exit 20)}}\n{{MAint\n|type=incomplete\n|mile=26.10\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=south|city1=Springfield}}\n|notes=Northbound access via Elm Street; Exit 27 on I-91 (formerly exit 21)}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Hatfield\n|mile=28.65\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=south|city1=Holyoke|location2=[[Springfield, Massachusetts|Springfield]]}}\n|notes=Exit 30 on I-91 (formerly exit 22)}}\n{{MAint\n|county=Franklin\n|cspan=9\n|location=Whately\n|lspan=3\n|mile=30.50\n|mile2=31.20\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=north|city1=Greenfield|location2=[[Brattleboro, Vermont|Brattleboro, VT]]}}\n|notes=Exit 32 on I-91 (formerly exit 23)}}\n{{MAint\n|type=incomplete\n|mile=33.70\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=south|city1=Holyoke|location2=[[Springfield, Massachusetts|Springfield]]}}\n|notes=No access to I-91 north; exit 35 on I-91 (formerly exit 24)}}\n{{MAint\n|type=concur\n|mile=33.90\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|116|dir1=south|city1=Sunderland|city2=Amherst}}\n|notes=Southern terminus of concurrency with Route 116}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Deerfield\n|type=concur\n|mile=34.80\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|116|dir1=north|I|91|to2=yes|city1=Conway|city2=Ashfield}}\n|notes=Northern terminus of concurrency with Route 116}}\n{{jctbridge\n|location_special=[[Deerfield River]]\n|mile=\n|bridge=Bridge}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Greenfield\n|lspan=2\n|mile=42.50\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|2A|city1=Athol}}\n|notes=Court Square, site of historic road marker}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=44.20\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|2|city1=Boston|city2=North Adams|I|91|to2=yes}}\n|notes=Diamond interchange}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Bernardston\n|lspan=2\n|type=concur\n|mile=49.00\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|10|dir1=north|city1=Northfield|I|91|to2=yes}}\n|notes=Northern terminus of concurrency with Route&nbsp;10}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=53.46\n|road={{jct|state=VT|US|5|dir1=north|city1=Brattleboro|city2=White River Junction}}\n|notes=Continuation into Vermont}}\n{{jctbtm|keys=concur,incomplete,toll}}\n\n==See also==\n* {{Portal-inline|United States}}\n* {{Portal-inline|U.S. Roads}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Attached KML}}\n{{Commons category|U.S. Route 5 in Massachusetts}}\n\n{{state detail page browse|type=US|route=5|state=Massachusetts|statebefore=Connecticut|stateafter=Vermont}}\n\n[[Category:U.S. Highways in Massachusetts|05]]\n[[Category:U.S. Route 5| Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Hampden County, Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Hampshire County, Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Franklin County, Massachusetts]]\n", "text_old": "{{highway detail hatnote|U.S. Route 5}}\n{{infobox road\n|state=MA\n|type=US\n|route=5\n|map={{maplink|frame=yes|plain=yes|frame-align=center|frame-width=290|frame-height=290|type=line|raw={{Wikipedia:Map data/Wikipedia KML/U.S. Route 5 in Massachusetts}}}}\n|map_custom=yes\n|map_notes=US 5 highlighted in red\n|length_mi=53.46\n|length_ref=<ref name=\"Google Maps US 5 MA\">{{google maps|url=https://maps.google.com/maps?saddr=US-7+N&daddr=US-7+N%2FSimonds+Rd&hl=en&sll=42.724695,-73.201904&sspn=0.068097,0.168743&geocode=FZuZgQIdrSOh-w%3BFdQ7jAIdWtui-w&t=h&mra=ls&z=9|title=U.S. Route 7 in Massachusetts|accessdate=2014-01-22}}</ref>\n|established=\n|direction_a=South\n|direction_b=North\n|terminus_a={{Jct|state=CT|US|5}} in [[Enfield, Connecticut|Enfield, CT]]\n|junction={{plainlist|\n*{{jct|state=MA|I|91}} in [[Springfield, Massachusetts|Springfield]]\n*{{jct|state=MA|MA|57}} in [[Agawam, Massachusetts|Agawam]]\n*{{jct|state=MA|US|20}} in [[West Springfield, Massachusetts|West Springfield]]\n*{{jct|state=MA|I|91|I|90}} in West Springfield\n*{{jct|state=MA|US|202}} in [[Holyoke, Massachusetts|Holyoke]]\n*{{jct|state=MA|MA|9|MA|10}} in [[Northampton, Massachusetts|Northampton]]\n*{{jct|state=MA|MA|2}} in [[Greenfield, Massachusetts|Greenfield]]\n*{{jct|state=MA|MA|10}} in [[Bernardston, Massachusetts|Bernardston]]\n}}\n|terminus_b={{Jct|state=VT|US|5}} in [[Guilford, Vermont|Guilford, VT]]\n|counties=[[Hampden County, Massachusetts|Hampden]], [[Hampshire County, Massachusetts|Hampshire]], [[Franklin County, Massachusetts|Franklin]]\n|previous_type=MA\n|previous_route=4\n|next_type=US\n|next_route=5A\n}}\n\n'''U.S. Route&nbsp;5''' ('''US&nbsp;5''') is a north\u2013south [[U.S. Highway]] extending from southern [[Connecticut]] to the northernmost part of [[Vermont]]. In [[Massachusetts]], the route travels {{convert|53.5|mi}}, paralleling the [[Connecticut River]] and [[Interstate 91 in Massachusetts|Interstate 91]] (I-91) through [[Hampden County, Massachusetts|Hampden]], [[Hampshire County, Massachusetts|Hampshire]], and [[Franklin County, Massachusetts|Franklin]] counties.\n\n==Route description==\nUS&nbsp;5 stays very close to the [[Connecticut River]] and [[Interstate 91]]. It enters the state at the town of [[Longmeadow, Massachusetts|Longmeadow]] on the east bank of the river going up to [[Springfield, Massachusetts|Springfield]]. In Springfield, US&nbsp;5 then overlaps with [[Interstate 91 in Massachusetts|Interstate 91]] (I-91) for about {{convert|0.5|mi|km}}, then separates as its own freeway crossing the Connecticut River on the South End Bridge into [[Agawam, Massachusetts|Agawam]]. The freeway portion travels for about {{convert|3.3|mi|km}} up to [[West Springfield, Massachusetts|West Springfield]]. From the town of [[Northampton, Massachusetts|Northampton]] up to [[Bernardston, Massachusetts|Bernardston]], US&nbsp;5 travels [[Concurrency (road)|concurrent]] with [[Massachusetts Route&nbsp;10]] (Route&nbsp;10 for {{convert|26|mi|km}}. US&nbsp;5 also passes through [[Holyoke, Massachusetts|Holyoke]], [[Hatfield, Massachusetts|Hatfield]], [[Whately, Massachusetts|Whately]], [[Deerfield, Massachusetts|Deerfield]], and [[Greenfield, Massachusetts|Greenfield]]. As in Connecticut, and Vermont US&nbsp;5 has many interchanges with the parallel I-91.\n{{Clear}}\n\n==Major intersections==\n{{mileposts}}\n{{jcttop|state=MA|length_ref=<ref name=\"Google Maps US 5 MA\"/>}}\n{{MAint\n|county=Hampden\n|cspan=15\n|location=Longmeadow\n|lspan=2\n|mile=0.00\n|road={{jct|state=CT|US|5|dir1=south|city1=Enfield|city2=Hartford}}\n|notes=Continuation into [[Connecticut]]}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=1.80\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|192|dir1=south|city1=East Longmeadow|location2=[[Stafford Springs, Connecticut|Stafford Springs, CT]]}}\n|notes=Northern terminus of Route 192}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Springfield\n|lspan=3\n|mile=3.50\n|type=concur\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=south|location1=[[Hartford, Connecticut|Hartford, CT]]}}\n|notes=Southern terminus of concurrency with I-91; Exit 1 on I-91}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=3.70\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|83|dir1=south|city1=Forest Park|city2=East Longmeadow}}\n|notes=Northern terminus of Route 83; Exit 2 on I-91}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=3.90\n|type=concur\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=north|city1=Greenfield}}\n|notes=Northern terminus of concurrency with I-91; Exit 3 on I-91}}\n{{jctbridge\n|location_special=[[Connecticut River]]\n|mile=\n|bridge=[[South End Bridge (Massachusetts)|South End Bridge]]}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Agawam\n|mile=4.60\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|57|dir1=west|city1=Agawam|city2=Southwick}}\n|notes=Rotary interchange; Eastern terminus of Route&nbsp;57}}\n{{MAint\n|location=West Springfield\n|lspan=4\n|mile=5.80\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|147|dir1=west|city1=West Springfield|city2=Agawam}}\n|notes=Rotary interchange; Eastern terminus of Route&nbsp;147, to [[Memorial Bridge (Massachusetts)|Memorial Bridge]]}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=7.00\n|road={{jct|state=MA|US|20|city1=Westfield|city2=Springfield}}\n|notes=Rotary interchange}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=9.30\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|I|391|to2=yes|city1=Holyoke}}\n|notes=Exit 10 on I-91 (formerly exit 13)}}\n{{MAint\n|type=toll\n|mile=10.80\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|I|90|city1=Greenfield|location2=[[Hartford, Connecticut|Hartford, CT]]|location3=[[Albany, New York|Albany, NY]]|city4=Boston}}\n|notes=Exit 45 on I-90 (formerly exit 4); Exit 11 on I-91 (formerly exit 14)}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Holyoke\n|lspan=4\n|mile=13.80\n|road={{jct|state=MA|US|202|I|91|to2=yes|city1=Westfield|city2=Southwick|city3=South Hadley}}\n|notes=}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=14.60\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|141|dir1=east|city1=Holyoke Center|city2=Chicopee Falls}}\n|notes=One-way eastbound}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=14.80\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|141|dir1=west|city1=Easthampton|I|91|to2=yes}}\n|notes=One-way westbound}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=15.00\n|road={{jct|state=MA|US|202|to1=yes|city1=South Hadley Falls|city2=Athol}}\n|notes=Via Lincoln Street}}\n{{MAint\n|county=Hampshire\n|cspan=5\n|location=Northampton\n|lspan=4\n|mile=21.90\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|city1=Greenfield|city2=Springfield}}\n|notes=Exit 23 on I-91 (formerly exit 18)}}\n{{MAint\n|type=concur\n|mile=22.90\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|9|MA|10|dir2=south|city1=Easthampton|city2=Pittsfield|city3=Amherst|city4=Worcester}}\n|notes=Southern terminus of concurrency with Route 10}}\n{{MAint\n|type=incomplete\n|mile=24.30\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=north|city1=Greenfield}}\n|notes=Northbound exit and southbound entrance; Exit 26 on I-91 (formerly exit 20)}}\n{{MAint\n|type=incomplete\n|mile=26.10\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=south|city1=Springfield}}\n|notes=Northbound access via Elm Street; Exit 27 on I-91 (formerly exit 21)}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Hatfield\n|mile=28.65\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=south|city1=Springfield|location2=[[Hartford, Connecticut|Hartford, CT]]}}\n|notes=Exit 30 on I-91 (formerly exit 22)}}\n{{MAint\n|county=Franklin\n|cspan=9\n|location=Whately\n|lspan=3\n|mile=30.50\n|mile2=31.20\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=north|city1=Greenfield|location2=[[Brattleboro, Vermont|Brattleboro, VT]]}}\n|notes=Exit 32 on I-91 (formerly exit 23)}}\n{{MAint\n|type=incomplete\n|mile=33.70\n|road={{jct|state=MA|I|91|dir1=south|city1=Springfield|location2=[[Hartford, Connecticut|Hartford, CT]]}}\n|notes=No access to I-91 north; exit 35 on I-91 (formerly exit 24)}}\n{{MAint\n|type=concur\n|mile=33.90\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|116|dir1=south|city1=Sunderland|city2=Amherst}}\n|notes=Southern terminus of concurrency with Route 116}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Deerfield\n|type=concur\n|mile=34.80\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|116|dir1=north|I|91|to2=yes|city1=Conway|city2=Ashfield}}\n|notes=Northern terminus of concurrency with Route 116}}\n{{jctbridge\n|location_special=[[Deerfield River]]\n|mile=\n|bridge=Bridge}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Greenfield\n|lspan=2\n|mile=42.50\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|2A|city1=Erving|city2=Athol}}\n|notes=Court Square, site of historic road marker}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=44.20\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|2|I|91|to2=yes|city1=Boston|city2=North Adams}}\n|notes=Diamond interchange}}\n{{MAint\n|location=Bernardston\n|lspan=2\n|type=concur\n|mile=49.00\n|road={{jct|state=MA|MA|10|dir1=north|city1=Northfield|I|91|to2=yes}}\n|notes=Northern terminus of concurrency with Route&nbsp;10}}\n{{MAint\n|mile=53.46\n|road={{jct|state=VT|US|5|dir1=north|city1=Brattleboro|city2=White River Junction}}\n|notes=Continuation into Vermont}}\n{{jctbtm|keys=concur,incomplete,toll}}\n\n==See also==\n* {{Portal-inline|United States}}\n* {{Portal-inline|U.S. Roads}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Attached KML}}\n{{Commons category|U.S. Route 5 in Massachusetts}}\n\n{{state detail page browse|type=US|route=5|state=Massachusetts|statebefore=Connecticut|stateafter=Vermont}}\n\n[[Category:U.S. Highways in Massachusetts|05]]\n[[Category:U.S. Route 5| Massachusetts]]\n