cy from the [[New York (state)|New York]] state line in [[Danbury, Connecticut|Danbury]] through the city\n: {{jct|country=USA|I|84|dab1=Pennsylvania\u2013Massachusetts}} with a concurrency through [[Danbury, Connecticut|Danbury]]\n: {{jct|country=USA|US|7}} with a concurrency from [[Danbury, Connecticut|Danbury]] to [[New Milford, Connecticut|New Milford]]\n: {{jct|country=USA|US|44}} with a concurrency from [[Canton, Connecticut|Canton]] to [[Avon, Connecticut|Avon]]\n\n;Massachusetts, New Hampshire, Maine\n{{jcttop|exit|state_col=state|length_ref=<ref name=\"NHDOT Roads\">{{cite web|url=http://www.granit.unh.edu/data/search?dset=roads_dot|title=NH Public Roads|author=Bureau of Planning & Community Assistance|date=February 20, 2015|website=|publisher=[[New Hampshire Department of Transportation]]|place=Concord, New Hampshire|accessdate=April 7, 2015}}</ref><ref name=\"NH Town Maps\">{{cite web|url=ftp://dot%2Ecity:streetmap@nhftp.admin.state.nh.us/2015_FULL_SIZE_PDFS/|title=Nodal Reference 2015, State of New Hampshire|author=Bureau of Planning & Community Assistance|date=April 3, 2015|website=|publisher=[[New Hampshire Department of Transportation]]|accessdate=April 7, 2015}}{{Dead link|date=July 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}\n*[ftp://dot%2Ecity:streetmap@nhftp.admin.state.nh.us/2015_FULL_SIZE_PDFS/RINDGE_Wallmap.pdf Town of Rindge, Cheshire County]{{Dead link|date=September 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}\n*[ftp://dot%2Ecity:streetmap@nhftp.admin.state.nh.us/2015_FULL_SIZE_PDFS/JAFFREY_Wallmap.pdf Town of Jaffrey, Cheshire County]{{Dead link|date=September 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}\n*[ftp://dot%2Ecity:streetmap@nhftp.admin.state.nh.us/2015_FULL_SIZE_PDFS/PETERBOROUGH_Wallmap.pdf Town of Peterborough, Hillsborough County]{{Dead link|date=September 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}\n*[ftp://dot%2Ecity:streetmap@nhftp.admin.state.nh.us/2015_FULL_SIZE_PDFS/HANCOCK_Wallmap.pdf Town of Han